article_title: Navy Investigating Alleged Ties Between Officers, Contractor
article_text:
A Navy investigation involving alleged ties between high-ranking officers and a military contractor is climbing higher into the service's ranks, with senior officials warning that more members are likely to be ensnared in the legal proceedings.

Last week, two admirals were denied access to classified information and placed on temporary leave as the Navy investigates allegations of corrupt business practices and bribes. Three Navy...
